
'''''The Boy Kumasenu''''' ni filime yasohotse muri  1952 yakorewe muri [[Gana]] n'abakozi ba firime yo mu [[Bwongereza]]<ref>BOY KUMASENU | colonialfilm <nowiki>http://www.colonialfilm.org.uk</nowiki> › node</ref>. Yakozwe kandi iyobowe na Sean Graham uhereye ku nyandiko ya Graham na John Wyllie.  Amanota yari Elisabeth Lutyens <ref>The BOY KUMASENU (1952) | BFI <nowiki>https://www2.bfi.org.uk</nowiki> › films-tv-people</ref>.  Filime yamenyekanye kandi igira ingaruka mubuzima rusange bwabaturage. Yagaragaje ibimenyetso by'ejo hazaza byatumye bijyana no kurwanya ubukoloni n'impinduka mu mibereho mu bwigenge bushya bwa [[Gana]]<ref>THE BOY KUMASENU - Torino Film Festival <nowiki>https://www.torinofilmfest.org</nowiki> › 16-torino-film-festival</ref>. 

== Umusaruro ==
'''''The Boy Kumasenu''''' yari filime ya mbere yagaragaye yakozwe na Gold Coast Film Unit, yashakaga gukora film zombi zigisha kandi zitanga amakuru kugirango zikwirakwizwe muri [[Gana]] ndetse no mumahanga<ref>Cinema and Highlife in the Gold Coast: The Boy Kumasenu ... <nowiki>https://www.tandfonline.com</nowiki> › ... › Volume 39, Issue 3

</ref>.   Uyu muyobozi yari Sean Graham, wari umunyeshuri w’umwanditsi w’inyandiko John Grierson, nubwo Graham yahisemo gukora cyane mu mvugo ya sinema izwi. <ref>'The Boy Kumasenu' and the work of the Gold Coast Film Unit <nowiki>https://www.africabib.org</nowiki> › rec</ref> Umucuranzi Guy Warren yari umwe mu bakinnyi, yakinnye nka Yeboah<ref>The Boy Kumasenu (1952) - Filmaffinity <nowiki>https://www.filmaffinity.com</nowiki> › film312612</ref>. 

Yafashwe amashusho mu 1950 na 1951 i [[Accra]], Kedze na Keta , hamwe nabakinnyi batabigize umwuga, ikorerwa i Londres.<ref>The Boy Kumasenu (1952) | MUBI <nowiki>https://mubi.com</nowiki> › films › the-boy-kumasenu</ref> Yerekanwe bwa mbere muri [[Gana]] mu 1952 ariko abayikoze bagize ikibazo cyo kuyikwirakwiza muri [[Gana]], kubera imyizerere y’uko Abanyafurika bakunda filime zo guhunga<ref>'The Boy Kumasenu' and the work of the Gold Coast Film Unit <nowiki>https://www.semanticscholar.org</nowiki> › paper › Modernity-and...</ref>. Ariko, byaje kugaragara ko ikunzwe cyane.   Yahawe impamyabumenyi n'Iserukiramuco rya Filime rya Venice kandi ryerekanwe bwa mbere mu [[Bwongereza]] mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Edinburgh 1952; yerekanwe no mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Berlin 1953. <ref>The Boy Kumasenu - Film (1952) - SensCritique <nowiki>https://www.senscritique.com</nowiki> › film</ref> Yatorewe igihembo cya Filime y'Ubwongereza ya Filime ya Filime nziza mu 1953<ref>The Boy Kumasenu (Film, 1952) - MovieMeter.nl <nowiki>https://www.moviemeter.nl</nowiki> › film</ref>. 

== Umugambi ==
Iyi filime ivuga amateka y’umuhungu witwa Kumasenu wimukiye mu mujyi wa [[Accra]] avuye mu mudugudu muto w’uburobyi, yatewe inkunga na mubyara we Agboh imigani ikabije y’ibitangaza byo mu mujyi. Ashonje<ref>The Boy Kumasenu (1953) - Sean Graham - AllMovie <nowiki>https://www.allmovie.com</nowiki> › movie › the-boy-kumasenu-v...</ref>, yiba umugati afatwa n'abapolisi, ariko arokorwa na muganga n'umugore we basanga akora. Agboh agerageza kwiba  Kumasenu muganga, ariko Kumasenu yanga imigambi ya mubyara we.<ref>The Boy Kumasenu (1952) - Video Detective <nowiki>https://www.videodetective.com</nowiki> › movie › the-boy-ku...</ref>
